What is Hard Working? Hard working is the job done with the best performance in terms of expense, time, labor, standardized and etc. Hence, for the same outcome1, whoever brings more effectiveness and efficiency is working hard instead of who simply spends more time.
We never promote a mule even it has been working for grinding all its life.
